**Do not skip commits on no repo-state diff.**

That conflicts with the staleness model. The beacon is not only a state snapshot; it is also a heartbeat. If the laptop successfully runs at `06:45`, `12:00`, and `17:15`, `latest.json.generated_at` must advance, even when every repo is unchanged.

