- laptop collector is healthy and nothing changed
- laptop is asleep
- launchd broke
- GitHub push broke

Since `generated_at` changes every successful run, `git diff --cached --quiet` will almost never be true anyway. If you suppress timestamp changes to make skip-commit work, you break freshness detection.

